{"tid":433162,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史最強］ 識睇波就知係佢","createTime":"2017-10-12T06:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T09:22:40.000Z","uid":46497,"like":107,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa3120c477791811606faf3b9f9c7eb6ef30b38","tid":433162,"uid":46497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/144923_ff9a0cdbeae88c13db945974765c9ea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F144923_ff9a0cdbeae88c13db945974765c9ea9.jpg&h=0b986c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5年前已經真真正正拎左足球大滿貫，亦係英超證明過自己<br />\n<br />\n曼聯：<br />\n07-08 英超<br />\n07-08 歐聯<br />\n<br />\n巴塞：<br />\n6次西甲<br />\n5次超級盃<br />\n3次歐聯<br />\n3次球會冠軍盃<br />\n<br />\n卻奧斯用同一個屈機班底贏2年歐聯<br />\nbig gay係轉會衛冕，07-08曼，08-09巴<br />\n足見佢既重要性<br />\n<br />\n跟哥帥第一年仲拎晒球會所有冠軍<br />\n一年六冠，可以拎既全部拎晒<br />\n<br />\n連登仔最睇重既國家隊<br />\n佢06年拎左u19歐洲國家盃<br />\n10，12 拎埋世界盃同歐國盃<br />\n<br />\n無數次入選最佳陣容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球王唔係佢係邊個？<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"1520d948485f94a64e04bd0c286fdae881f2cc7c","tid":433162,"uid":34571,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"未拎過金球"},{"pid":"4e3daa707b5e6cb0d2b4d39be1ed990caf6e3f30","tid":433162,"uid":34571,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:59:24.000Z","msg":"卡卡"},{"pid":"529bd5a68cc12716d07786fc8a03d87ee04f03f1","tid":433162,"uid":46497,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"牙朗 美斯當年都係跟佢搵食"},{"pid":"0f79acde74c607f254b2aab1cc32a9ccc392ade9","tid":433162,"uid":46497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡卡</blockquote><br />\n有冇衛冕過歐聯<br />\n有冇一年6冠<br />\n有冇係英超證明過自己？"},{"pid":"e80d91f11bb5c21145c22b094227ae950bd4549c","tid":433162,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20